nternet through Nest Connect. So you can use the Nest app to lock and unlock your door from anywhere, create passcodes for people you trust, and get alerts whenever someone comes and goes.</span></aside><aside class="oTSVsc"><span class="rIbWHd"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/GLVUEYL1Aua1w4-fPT2rX_r8-Q7aS_iyAWcYs1mUQx4BhEluyQUrCZySizBQJOmyseOt9x8soc2mwo5jfnqYeIs1ksBr7T_6nzs" alt="How it works" class="JpItMb"/></span></aside></article></div></a></li><li class="TIlrKb" ssk='15:Google Home App'><a href="https://store.google.com/intl/en/ideas/articles/google-home-app-updates/" jsaction="click:ufFX6e;" class="sWgry" aria-label="Google Home App" data-tracking-module-name="mobile-nav-tray-section-Discover" data-tracking-label="section-detailed:Google Home App:1" data-tracking-index="1" data-tracking-action="/category/connected_home&gt;&gt;https://store.google.com/intl/en/ideas/articles/google-home-app-updates/" data-tracking-url="https://store.google.com/intl/en/ideas/articles/google-home-app-updates/"><div data-component-name="box" class="gQjUFd NGrerf fXTCsc UiYyRd" style="padding:8px;border-radius:24px"><article class="ri9Fr"><aside class="oTSVsc"><span class="BhjvRe">Google Home App</span><span class="eUe8V">The redesigned Google Home app makes it easier to control your smart home devices, wherever you are.</span></aside><aside class="oTSVsc"><span class="rIbWHd"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/sBnuaW-Es87DpbyRqX8Ubt3nMOlmSvqWdm0sR7JTvIVLlKsLNEL7O53nh3DaVSVNwfYtsPWyYjTa62oHQb1BwYa5ylGRY4ibf5N2" alt="Google Home App" class="JpItMb"/></span></aside></article></div></a></li></ul></div></aside></div></section></li><li class="Ww44I" ssk='6:i:WiFi'><a href="#" role="button" data-item-index="7" aria-label="WiFi" jsaction="click:jmgg6" class="DmTXI" data-target-stack-id="primary-Smart Home-WiFi" data-tracking-module-name="mobile-nav-tray-item-secondary-category" data-tracking-label="category:WiFi:7" data-tracking-index="7" data-tracking-action="/catego