I powers many of Pixel&#39;s helpful features on the Pixel Camera, from Magic Eraser to searching what you see with Google Lens, and on the device itself from Clear Calling to Hold for Me and call blocking.</span></aside><aside class="oTSVsc"><span class="rIbWHd"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/EsolNlYjvVC8ktHQV6gdQ5QkjBZpml5escbzZHB1puXpyW9_z5dHmN7aIQN8hKPn1Nou6kxbnF4rgbkc9Iar3A1AFrTgpzPwaA" alt="Gemini on Pixel" class="JpItMb"/></span></aside></article></div></a></li><li class="TIlrKb" ssk='12:Pixel Camera'><a href="https://store.google.com/intl/en/ideas/pixel-camera-features/" jsaction="click:XHJpEb" aria-label="Pixel Camera" data-tracking-module-name="desktop-tray-section-Discover" data-tracking-label="section-detailed:Pixel Camera:2" data-tracking-index="2" data-tracking-url="https://store.google.com/intl/en/ideas/pixel-camera-features/" data-tracking-action="/category/phones&gt;https://store.google.com/intl/en/ideas/pixel-camera-features/" class="sWgry" ssk='13:Pixel Camera2'><div data-component-name="box" class="gQjUFd NGrerf fXTCsc UiYyRd" style="padding:8px;border-radius:24px"><article class="ri9Fr"><aside class="oTSVsc"><span class="BhjvRe">Pixel Camera</span><span class="eUe8V">Focus on the moment. Pixel will get the picture. All of your photos will look stunning.</span></aside><aside class="oTSVsc"><span class="rIbWHd"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/EYTAbmiX9YBYCI2szDiFxpe9pngmc5FXenW6xkp-eE2aKql77pgQ9Oe6BfagExu81CFDQ3mjaslB9orbYnvR1zgzo5mJXPkZgbs" alt="Pixel Camera" class="JpItMb"/></span></aside></article></div></a></li><li class="TIlrKb" ssk='11:Pixel Drops'><a href="/magazine/pixel_drop?hl=en-US" jsaction="click:XHJpEb" aria-label="Pixel Drops" data-tracking-module-name="desktop-tray-section-Discover" data-tracking-label="section-detailed:Pixel Drops:3" data-tracking-index="3" data-tracking-url="/magazine/pixel_drop" data-tracking-action="/category/phones&gt;/magazine/pixel_drop" class="sWgry" ssk='12:Pixel Drops3'><div data-